{"tid":2007264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2020初夏 - 日文班","createTime":"2020-05-08T08:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T18:38:23.000Z","uid":2771,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6dca110869ee4f5d5441217b75cc8e92a1ee3398","tid":2007264,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"大家好呀！<br />\n首先好多謝大家之前報左我地嘅課堂，話咁快又完左一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然之前疫情嚴峻，我地不得不轉爲網上上堂，但好感謝各位同學對我地不離不棄，就算無得現場練會話都好，都十分認真上堂、溫習同做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊我地都會認真評估狀況，係情況許可之下，希望可以係返課室度上堂！<br />\n<br />\n其實我地都好想每次都開到初級班比想學嘅巴打絲打<br />\n但基於人手同時間有限，今次暫時未有初級班，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過左幾期，已經陸陸續續有唔少完成左25課嘅同學仔，黎緊可能會係今年年尾考N5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果各位嘅程度差唔多係大家的日本語25課，歡迎報我地嘅N5班，爲年尾嘅考試做好準備！<br />\n另外如果大家報左7月N5嘅，亦歡迎同我地傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Form:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/jHXq15Yts4s2sq9H6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FjHXq15Yts4s2sq9H6&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=64a357d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/jHXq15Yts4s2sq9H6</a>"},{"pid":"7afa73717ebff2f6f9a0d7d2c572a11640c8dea3","tid":2007264,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"【郭偉强找數】<br />\n<br />\n呼籲集體投訴社工之恥郭偉强蓄意襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉强社工註冊編號：11071<br />\n罪行：普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n下載「社會工作者註冊局」投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2FDocuments%2Fcomplaint.pdf&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=b9a38214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"152f46901ea3be818648ce1126560b19308aca28","tid":2007264,"uid":2771,